## Workflow Phases

When using the 9-phase workflow:

| Phase | Name | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| 1 | Understand | Gather requirements, analyze scope |
| 2 | Design | Technical architecture, component design |
| 3 | UI Breakdown | UI/UX analysis, component hierarchy |
| 4 | Test Plan | Test strategy, test cases |
| 5a | TDD RED | Write failing tests first |
| 5b | TDD GREEN | Implement to pass tests |
| 5c | TDD REFACTOR | Improve code quality |
| 6 | Review | Code review, quality checks |
| 7 | Verify | QA validation, acceptance testing |
| 8 | Document | Documentation updates |
| 9 | Share | Notifications, knowledge sharing |

**Phase details:** `.cursor/workflows/`

